## IRoles.editor property

> This API is provided as a preview for developers and may change based on feedback that we receive. Do not use this API in a production environment.
> 

The editor role allows the wallet to edit data in the [DatastoreModule](./sdk.datastoremodule.md)<!-- -->.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
editor: "editor";
```
